long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This SEO extension makes it easy to identify and review all external links on a page, providing insights into anchor text relevance, and dofollow/nofollow status. Additionally, the extension displays a complete list of all headings (H1-H6) on the page, helping you ensure proper content structure and alignment with SEO best practices. Perfect for quick on-page SEO analysis, this tool streamlines link and heading evaluation to optimize content performance.
